Package com.example.mooderation.auth.base

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IAuthentication
    Interface for authentication credentials returned by successfully logging in with an IAuthenticator.
    IAuthenticator
    Interface for a class that wraps an authentication system.
    IAuthenticator.AuthenticationResultListener
    Listener that yields an AuthenticationResult when authentication either succeeds or fails.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AuthenticationResult
    Contains the results of an authentication query.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description

    Wraps errors generated by an IAuthenticator.
